the king of tonga a bananaexporting 
south pacific island nation with 443 cars wants all the tires 
washington state can spare 
not to put them on cars but to burn them 
king taufaahau tupou iv sees mounds of rubber as the answer to 
his kingdoms quest for energy independence and is pounding on the 
